headline: 4 Utility Stocks to Buy From the Thriving Electric Power Industry
summary: Expected rise in electric consumption, along with an increase in prices, bodes well for the prospect of the Utility-Electric Power industry. Top-ranked utilities like DUK, D, ETR and CNP are set to benefit from strong demand from their customer base.

headline: Entergy elects retired Admiral Frank Caldwell to board of directors
summary: The board of directors for Entergy Corporation today announced the election of retired Admiral Frank Caldwell as an independent director, effective Nov. 1.

headline: Gas continues to dominate Entergy plans as data center pipeline grows
summary: The company has agreements for several notable large load projects with Google and Meta and expects substantial load growth from commercial and industrial customers through 2029.
